Mak cik. Mak cik tak apa-apa? Mak cik.

137
00:10:40,011 --> 00:10:41,279
- Dapat pun kamu. - Mak cik.

138
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:44,590
Ini tak adil. Itu menipu namanya.

139
00:10:44,591 --> 00:10:46,745
Kamu yang tipu dulu.

140
00:10:46,751 --> 00:10:49,689
Tidak, tunggu. Lepaskan saya.

141
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:52,289
- Aduhai. Penatnya. - Tolong lepaskan saya.

142
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:53,625
Mak cik, tolonglah!

143
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:08,206
Duduk.

144
00:11:08,310 --> 00:11:10,275
Saya tak nak duduk di atas lantai.

145
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:16,279
Kadang-kadang dia boleh jadi sangat kebaratan.

146
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,986
Dia jarang lakukannya, tapi dia buat tadi.

147
00:11:25,930 --> 00:11:28,456
Biar saya perkenalkan diri saya, teman lelaki Dong Kyung.

148
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:32,165
Saya Kang Soo Ja. Saya mak cik Dong Kyung.

149
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:35,466
Ya, dia mak cik saya, Kang Soo Ja.

150
00:11:35,601 --> 00:11:36,836
"Teman lelaki"?

151
00:11:37,711 --> 00:11:39,270
Banyak yang saya dengar tentang awak.

152
00:11:39,271 --> 00:11:41,306
Banyak yang awak dengar tentang dia? Daripada siapa?

153
00:11:51,721 --> 00:11:53,250
Sun Kyung, budak tak guna.

154
00:11:53,251 --> 00:11:55,590
Saya minta maaf atas apa yang berlaku tadi.

155
00:11:55,591 --> 00:11:57,056
Tentu awak terkejut.

156
00:11:57,190 --> 00:11:59,726
Tak apa. Jangan risau.

157
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,995
Tapi di mana rumah awak?

158
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:06,625
Sekarang dah lewat.

159
00:12:06,830 --> 00:12:07,840
Saya tinggal...

160
00:12:07,841 --> 00:12:11,096
Ya, betul. Hari dah lewat.

161
00:12:11,141 --> 00:12:12,809
- Awak baliklah. - Tapi awak suruh saya duduk.

162
